.DT
is_member
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
is_member

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_member -  This function allows you to check whether a person is a member of a group.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_member(string name,
object person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the group
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person you want to check for membership

.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if he is a member, 0 if he isn't (or the group doesn't exist)


.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function allows you to check whether a person is a member
of a group.

.EP

